========================================================================
PART 2: μ_v(T) IN TERMS OF CYCLE STRUCTURE
========================================================================

For each vertex v, μ_v = number of HP through-v cycles = (H(T)-H(T-v))/2
Q: How does μ_v relate to the cycles THROUGH v in the conflict graph?

--- n = 4 ---
  H=  1 Hv=  1 μ_v=  0 | through_v=0 not_through_v=0 cycles(T-v)=0
  H=  3 Hv=  1 μ_v=  1 | through_v=1 not_through_v=0 cycles(T-v)=0
